## 🚀 Running the Server

The server uses standard `stdio` (stdin/stdout) transport protocol for communication.

### Run with Python directly:

```bash
python main.py
```

### Running with BobShell Helper (Auto-Setup & Run)

A helper script has been generated to verify dependencies and start the server:

```bash
# On Linux/macOS:
chmod +x run_server.sh
./run_server.sh

# On Windows:
run_server.bat
```

